---
/**
 * CTAセクション（お問い合わせ導線）
 */
---

<section class="cta-section">
  <span class="cta-label">Contact</span>
  <h2 class="cta-title">まずは、お気軽にご相談ください</h2>
  <p class="cta-sub">相談・お見積り、すべて無料です</p>
  <p class="cta-desc">
    「どこに相談すればいいかわからない」という方も大歓迎。<br />
    専門スタッフが丁寧にお答えします。
  </p>
  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-cta-mail">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z" />
      </svg>
      メールでお問い合わせ
    </a>
    <a href="tel:0766-75-8008" class="btn-cta-tel">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M6.6 10.8c1.4 2.8 3.8 5.1 6.6 6.6l2.2-2.2c.3-.3.7-.4 1-.2 1.1.4 2.3.6 3.6.6.6 0 1 .4 1 1V20c0 .6-.4 1-1 1-9.4 0-17-7.6-17-17 0-.6.4-1 1-1h3.5c.6 0 1 .4 1 1 0 1.3.2 2.5.6 3.6.1.3 0 .7-.2 1L6.6 10.8z" />
      </svg>
      <span class="btn-cta-tel-inner">
        <span class="btn-cta-tel-label">お電話でのご相談</span>
        <span class="btn-cta-tel-num">0766-75-8008</span>
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    padding: 100px 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #001850 100%);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -160px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px; height: 700px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74, 144, 217, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cta-label::before,
  .cta-label::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 42px);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-jp);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .cta-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-cta-mail {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 18px 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    transition: var(--transition-base);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .btn-cta-mail:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .btn-cta-tel {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    transition: var(--transition-base);
  }

  .btn-cta-tel:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-cta-tel-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .btn-cta-tel-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .btn-cta-tel-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* === Responsive === */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-section { padding: 72px 16px; }

    .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }

    .btn-cta-mail,
    .btn-cta-tel {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
